# Vortex source commit that produced this pkg.
#
# When `vortex_source_commit_verified` is `false`, the commit is a best-guess
# from vortex GuestTools/ git history at the time of vendoring — the actual
# build was not recorded. Run `scripts/update-vortex-pkg.sh` to rebuild from
# a known commit and flip this to `true`.
#
# Note: the bundled Mach-O binaries are ad-hoc (linker-only) signed, so
# byte-exact rebuild reproducibility is not guaranteed even from the same
# commit. The pkg_sha256 check is the authoritative integrity gate.
